snippet: The United States government has petitioned the Irish High Court to extradite an Algerian man living in Ireland on terrorism charges relating to a plot to kill a Swedish artist.
lead_paragraph: The United States government has petitioned the Irish High Court to extradite an Algerian man living in Ireland on terrorism charges relating to a plot to kill a Swedish artist.

headline.main: Ireland: Suspect in Terrorism Case Faces Extradition to U.S.
headline.print_headline: Ireland: Suspect in Terrorism Case Faces Extradition to U.S.
